It's okay.

299
00:15:30,400 --> 00:15:32,160
I'm the one who should apologize.

300
00:15:32,160 --> 00:15:33,890
I made you take such a huge risk,

301
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:36,040
only to get eliminated this way.

302
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,480
But something already happened to Shasha.

303
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:40,120
I can't let you take any more risks.

304
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:41,450
It doesn't matter to me.

305
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:44,400
It's just a pity about that ring.

306
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:46,600
Zhu Xiaoyu got off too easily.

307
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,440
That one is fake.

308
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:52,160
This one

309
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,300
is the real one.

310
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:56,400
You.

311
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:58,960
There is something wrong with her ring.

312
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,220
I knew there was something off about her.

313
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,130
Sure enough.

314
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:04,820
She has been secretly filming us.

315
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,680
Secretly filming me.

316
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,640
That's great.

317
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:17,440
My efforts these past few days haven't been in vain after all.

318
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:19,840
You've done enough.

319
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,000
Leave the rest

320
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:21,760
to me.

321
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:22,840
That won't do.

322
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:25,290
It's too dangerous for you to go alone.

323
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,280
Maybe

324
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:29,160
there's someone

325
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,020
who can help me.

326
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:07,079
Excuse me.

327
00:17:07,079 --> 00:17:08,000
Hello.

328
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,480
I'm a freshman in the PE department.

329
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,540
Lin Yi'ang, right?

330
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:12,079
You know me?

331
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:13,200
Am I that famous?

332
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:15,319
I came specifically for you.

333
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:17,400
I wanted to ask you about something.

334
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:19,540
I'll tell you whatever I know.

335
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:22,119
I heard you are Zhang Chao's roommate.

336
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:22,760
May I ask

337
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,359
where he went?

338
00:17:25,520 --> 00:17:26,599
Zhang Chao?

339
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:27,480
Let me tell you,

340
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:29,280
Zhang Chao is my best...

341
00:17:29,280 --> 00:17:30,160
Best...

342
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:38,840
I'm sorry.

343
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,940
Something did happen.

344
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:50,370
No wonder I couldn't reach him.

345
00:17:50,520 --> 00:17:51,080
Yeah.

346
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,360
It's been a week.

347
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:55,120
It's all that bastard Lin Jiaming's fault.

348
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:55,960
But

349
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,600
the principal has been informed.

350
00:17:57,600 --> 00:18:00,080
Mr. Chen and Dr. He have been running around for this.

351
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:00,880
I believe

352
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:01,480
before long,

353
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,940
there should be good news.

354
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,560
Lin Jiaming.

355
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,200
You've been at Jieda

356
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:31,800
for a while now, haven't you?

357
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,480
Are you getting used to it there?

358
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:38,010
Everyone takes good care of me.

359
00:18:38,080 --> 00:18:42,740
I'm also familiarizing myself with the company's business as quickly as possible.

360
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:45,960
A teacher of mine once told me,

361
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,280
When playing chess,

362
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:50,160
there are no magic moves for the whole game.

363
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:51,760
Running a company is the same.

364
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:53,800
Don't be too hasty.

365
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:56,260
You need to know how to accumulate strength.

366
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,440
You seem to

367
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:59,240
rarely mention this teacher.

368
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:04,920
Now that you mention it,

369
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,800
I haven't seen him in a while.

370
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:11,000
I'll go to the Lin Family Sanatorium in a few days.

371
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,040
If you need anything,

372
00:19:12,040 --> 00:19:13,770
go find your brother Chaoyang.

373
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,680
Then can I go with you?

374
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,640
Why do you suddenly want to go there?

375
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:33,080
Because

376
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:36,560
doesn't Qiong University have a

377
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:39,020
College Student Mental Health Foundation?

378
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,040
And I want

379
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:42,520
to learn from their experience.

380
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:45,560
Alright.

381
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,690
You've made progress, boy.

382
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:54,940
Come with me tomorrow.

383
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:56,610
Thanks, Dad.

384
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:01,280
Zhang Chao.

385
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,130
It's time to meet again.

386
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,280
I'm here.

387
00:20:57,240 --> 00:20:58,320
Why do you look

388
00:20:58,760 --> 00:21:00,000
so unhappy?

389
00:21:01,120 --> 00:21:02,050
Where is Yueyue?

390
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,320
Why does it have to be her?

391
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,460
I have everything she has.

392
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:08,040
And I have

393
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,640
what she doesn't.

394
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,680
Is that so?

395
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,760
Baby.

396
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:29,560
Let Jin take good care of you.

397
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:34,610
Why are you here?

398
00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:38,920
Waiting for my boyfriend, of course.

399
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:41,600
Does someone like you need a boyfriend?

400
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:44,040
Don't you just need a backer?

401
00:22:45,120 --> 00:22:46,400
You are right.

402
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,000
Master Lin, you're handsome

403
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,260
and from a good family.

404
00:22:50,600 --> 00:22:51,600
Everyone sucks up to you

405
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,200
because of your background.

406
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,200
So you never believe

407
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:56,800
that anyone truly loves you.

408
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:59,020
But I am different.

409
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,080
I truly love you.

410
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:02,920
Do you know why?

411
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:05,680
Because deep down, we are the same.

412
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,520
We're both scum.

413
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:10,360
So,

414
00:23:11,840 --> 00:23:14,240
I am the only one

415
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:15,700
who understands you best.

416
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:29,480
Hello?

417
00:23:30,840 --> 00:23:31,520
Bai Qiu.

418
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:32,960
Go ahead.

419
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:35,240
Okay.

420
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:36,520
No problem.

421
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,040
Sure.

422
00:23:38,040 --> 00:23:39,040
No problem.

423
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:40,080
Okay.

424
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:41,040
Anything works.

425
00:23:41,040 --> 00:23:42,280
Okay.

426
00:24:07,560 --> 00:24:08,290
You're here.

427
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,320
I didn't expect you to take the initiative

428
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:13,760
to ask me out after all these years.

429
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:14,880
Tell me, what is it?

430
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:17,140
You were the one who got Zhang Chao

431
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:19,680
locked up in the sanatorium, right?

432
00:24:24,360 --> 00:24:26,040
The first time you take the initiative to ask me out,

433
00:24:26,040 --> 00:24:27,900
and it's because of someone else.

434
00:24:28,160 --> 00:24:29,720
Why?

435
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:32,900
Do you see this?

436
00:24:33,560 --> 00:24:34,280
Half a month ago,

437
00:24:34,280 --> 00:24:35,240
I had over a dozen large and small

438
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:37,440
wounds like this on my face.

439
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,880
I've already shown enough mercy

440
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:40,800
by not sending him to the police station.

441
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:42,760
Now that you've taught him a lesson,

442
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:44,520
it's about time to let him go.

443
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:49,810
Why are you helping him?

444
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:51,600
Or in other words,

445
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:53,240
why should I help you?

446
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:56,120
Before,

447
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:57,920
he did me a favor.

448
00:24:59,320 --> 00:25:01,320
Consider this returning the favor.

449
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:05,480
Helping you means you owe me a favor?

450
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:07,890
Then if I help you this time,

451
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,960
will you owe me a favor too?

452
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:10,680
Of course,

453
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,080
as long as it's within my power.

454
00:25:12,080 --> 00:25:12,840
Okay,

455
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:14,900
then come home with me.

456
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:17,450
Pretend I didn't say anything.

457
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:19,520
Let go.

458
00:25:20,280 --> 00:25:21,960
What do you think we are going to do at my place?

459
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:23,160
What else could we do?

460
00:25:24,560 --> 00:25:25,960
You're overthinking it.

461
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,120
Besides,

462
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:30,520
you're asking me for help right now.

463
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:31,920
When asking for help,

464
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:33,960
you should have the right attitude.

465
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:36,090
Let's go.

466
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:55,930
Watch your step.

467
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,200
Please.

468
00:26:29,280 --> 00:26:29,880
How is it?

469
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,320
Isn't he cute?

470
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:43,770
I saved this little hamster

471
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:45,800
from a snake's mouth.

472
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:47,800
I didn't expect

473
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:48,930
it to live this long.

474
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:57,520
I didn't expect you to have some humanity left.

475
00:26:59,520 --> 00:27:00,760
So in your heart,

476
00:27:01,560 --> 00:27:03,120
what kind of person am I?

477
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:07,840
You asked me to come to your house

478
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:09,080
just to show me this?

479
00:27:14,120 --> 00:27:15,360
When I was ten,

480
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:16,840
at my birthday party,

481
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:19,100
I invited you to my house and you refused.

482
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:21,360
When I was 14 and beaten by my dad,

483
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:22,810
I bought two tickets

484
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,920
and ran to your downstairs,

485
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:26,520
wanting you to leave with me,

486
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,450
but you thought I was crazy.

487
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:31,800
At the prom when we were 18,

488
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:34,050
I wanted to ask you to dance,

489
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:35,760
but you'd rather

490
00:27:36,600 --> 00:27:37,760
dance with girls

491
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:39,280
than touch my hand.

492
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:41,200
Is this...

493
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:43,740
This is the song from the prom that night.

494
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:47,420
I've been thinking about this

495
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,610
for a very long time.

496
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,880
So you mean

497
00:27:58,080 --> 00:27:59,140
if I dance with you,

498
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:00,800
you'll let Zhang Chao go?

499
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,220
What are you doing?

500
00:29:26,360 --> 00:29:27,560
Psycho.

501
00:29:30,120 --> 00:29:31,320
Be my girlfriend.

502
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:32,440
You're crazy.

503
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:33,320
As long as you are my girlfriend,

504
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:34,650
I can give you anything.

505
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:38,520
You can never give me what I want.

506
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:42,140
Is it because of Zhang Chao again?

507
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,730
I don't care what you think,

508
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:45,200
or whether you let him go.

509
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,280
This ends here.

510
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:49,570
I will never ask you for help again.

511
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:54,800
I promise you.
